sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant Platform as Platform Ingress<br/>(TLS Termination)
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails Pipeline
    participant ExtAPI as External Guardrail APIs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LLM as LLM Inference Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails Pipeline

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails (/v1/chat/completions)
        Client->>Platform: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS (TLS 1.2+)
        Platform->>Server: HTTP :8000<br/>(plaintext, platform-level auth)
        Server->>InputRails: Process user message<br/>(local pipeline)
        InputRails->>ExtAPI: Safety checks (optional)<br/>HTTPS :443, API Key Auth
        ExtAPI-->>InputRails: Safety verdict
        alt Input rails PASS
            Server->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS :443, Bearer Token (forwarded)
            LLM-->>Server: LLM response
            Server->>OutputRails: Process LLM response<br/>(local pipeline)
            OutputRails->>ExtAPI: Output safety checks (optional)<br/>HTTPS :443, API Key Auth
            ExtAPI-->>OutputRails: Safety verdict
            alt Output rails PASS
                Server-->>Platform: JSON response (guarded)
                Platform-->>Client: HTTPS response
            else Output rails FAIL
                Server-->>Platform: Blocked/modified response
                Platform-->>Client: Safety intervention message
            end
        else Input rails FAIL
            Server-->>Platform: Blocked response (no LLM call)
            Platform-->>Client: Safety intervention message
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 2: Guardrail-Only Check (/v1/guardrail/checks) [Fork-Specific]
        Client->>Platform: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTPS (TLS 1.2+)
        Platform->>Server: HTTP :8000<br/>(plaintext)
        alt role = user/system
            Server->>InputRails: Route to Input Rails
            InputRails->>ExtAPI: Safety checks (if configured)<br/>HTTPS :443, API Key Auth
            ExtAPI-->>InputRails: Safety verdict
            InputRails-->>Server: Rail status per message
        else role = assistant
            Server->>OutputRails: Route to Output Rails
            OutputRails->>ExtAPI: Safety checks (if configured)<br/>HTTPS :443, API Key Auth
            ExtAPI-->>OutputRails: Safety verdict
            OutputRails-->>Server: Rail status per message
        end
        Server-->>Platform: Rail evaluation results (no LLM call)
        Platform-->>Client: HTTPS response with rail status
    end
